0.2.name: wordpress/ajaxify-faqtastic
0.2.description:
Used to add AJAX open close effects to the FAQ-Tastic WordPress plugin.

Please note that this plugin does nothing on its own. This plugin requires the FAQ-Tastic Lite WordPress plugin that can be found at http://faq-tastic.com/faqtastic-lite-free/.

Javascript libraries used: jQuery. jQuery is used from the WordPress sources.
